AMENDEDANALYSIS
Thisbill:
I. Enables regional, conservation, and energy resource planning for habitat strongholds and
wildlifecorridors.
II. Creates a commission to study transferring ownership of the Winnipesaukee River Basin
programtoanalternativeauthority.
III. Creates the position of director of the Winnipesaukee River Basin Program within the
departmentofenvironmentalservices.
